        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Instantly, Fritz snatched it from his hand, waved it over his head, shouted, \"Charge, brothers, fill up the ranks!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
