        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "She fell on her knees, and snatching the kerchief from her throat and breast, strove to stanch the blood that welled from his heart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
