        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "He looked up into her eyes, with such love in them as made her choke with emotion, and he said faintly: \"Muetterchen, do not grieve for me; we have stormed the redoubt, the day is ours.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
