        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Moreover, the sun was shining brightly, and it gleamed over a new parish church, of cut white stone, very stately, with a gilded spire, with windows of wondrous lacework.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
