        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "They say that he values it above gold.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "\"Oh! he is a good man is Johann; he was always a good and serious boy, and never happy without a pencil in his hand.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "You mark what I say.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Some day hence, when he is dead, there will be a statue erected in his honour here in this market place, to commemorate the one famous man that has been produced by Siebenstein.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "But see-see!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Here he comes to the dedication of the new church.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "All the men present plucked off their hats to him, and made way for him as he advanced.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "All at once his eye encountered that of Anna.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "He might have been, God had so purposed; but thou madest His purpose of none effect.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Thou didst send his soul over the mill wheel.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "And then faintly, as from a far distance, sounded in her ear the call of the cuckoo-three.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "The magnificent new church had shrivelled up to the original mean little edifice Anna had known all her life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "The square was deserted, the cold faint glimmer of coming dawn was visible over the eastern mountain tops, but stars still shone in the sky.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "With a cry of pain, like a wounded beast, Anna ran hither and thither seeking a refuge, and then fled to the one home and resting place of the troubled soul-the church.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "She thrust open the swing door, pushed in, sped over the uneven floor, and flung herself on her knees before the altar.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Then the priest turned himself about, and said, \"Oremus.\" And she knew him-he was her own son-her Joseph, named after his dear father.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "\"Cursed is the unfruitful field!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "\"Cursed is the empty house!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "\"Cursed is the fishless lake!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Woe! woe!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000044_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000044_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "woe!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Two years ago, during the first week in June, an English traveller arrived at Siebenstein and put up at the \"Krone,\" where, as he was tired and hungry, he ordered an early supper.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000047_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000047_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "She had in her hand a small basket.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "He was struck with her face.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "His eyes followed her as she walked towards the mill stream, and there she took her place on the wooden bridge that crossed it, leaning over the handrail, and looking down into the water.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000051_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000051_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "An impulse of curiosity and of interest led him to follow her at a distance, and he saw her pick a flower, a pansy, out of her basket, and drop it into the current, which caught and carried it forward.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000051_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000051_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "Then she took a second, and allowed it to fall into the water.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000051_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000051_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "After that she bowed her head on her hands; her grey hair fell over them, and she broke into a paroxysm of weeping.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "The traveller, standing by the stream, saw the seven pansies swept down, and one by one pass over the revolving wheel and vanish.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "\"That,\" replied the man, \"is the Mother of Pansies.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6758_72288_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6758/72288/6758_72288_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6758",
        "content": "\"The Mother of Pansies!\" he repeated.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
